---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hello World!" description="Introductory announcement from Dog Expert Tech.">
  <article class="post-container">
    <header class="post-header">
      <a class="back-link" href="/blog/">← Back to Blog</a>
      <h1>Hello World!</h1>
      <p class="post-meta">August 2, 2025 | By Dog Expert Tech</p>
    </header>

    <img src="/gallery/assets/wallpapers/Nebula-2.png" alt="Blog Post Image" class="post-image" loading="lazy" />

    <div class="post-body">
      <p>Hello! This is my first blog post on Dog Expert Tech. I'm excited to start this journey!</p>
      <p>In this blog, I will be sharing useful information, tech tips, and guides on how to fix common computer problems and more.</p>
      <p>I will be posting new content very soon, so stay tuned and keep an eye on the blog!</p>
    </div>

    <footer class="post-footer">
      <div id="google_translate_element"></div>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Dog Expert Tech</p>
    </footer>
  </article>

  <script type="text/javascript">
    function googleTranslateElementInit() {
      new google.translate.TranslateElement({
        pageLanguage: 'en',
        includedLanguages: 'en,et,ru',
        layout: google.translate.TranslateElement.InlineLayout.SIMPLE
      }, 'google_translate_element');
    }
  </script>
  <script src="//translate.google.com/translate_a/element.js?cb=googleTranslateElementInit" async defer></script>
</Layout>

<style>
  .post-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .post-header {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #005f73;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .post-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .post-meta {
    color: #666;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .post-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
  }

  .post-body {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  body.dark .post-body {
    background: #161616;
    color: #ddd;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .post-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .post-footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  body.dark .post-footer {
    color: #aaa;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .post-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>